short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A Browser Extension which gives different filetypes different icons, and code color theme to GitHub and Octotree for free.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Octotree is a very useful extension when using Github. My add-on brings icon themes and code themes to use with Octotree and Github for free. Below are the themes that this extension provides.

Icons theme
- Material Icons Theme
- Atom Icons Theme

Code corlor themes
- Default (Default Github theme)
